# MetaIC AI - Cursor Rules

## Project Structure
- `backend/` - Node.js/Express backend API
- `src/` - Uni-app Vue 3 frontend
- `website/` - Landing page (metaic.ai)
- `figma-import/` - Figma design files

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Vue 3, Uni-app, TypeScript, SCSS
- Backend: Node.js, Express, TypeScript
- Database: PostgreSQL
- AI: Google Gemini Pro

## Key Files
- `PRD.md` - Product Requirements Document
- `backend/API_DESIGN.md` - API documentation
- `backend/DATABASE_SCHEMA.md` - Database schema
- `website/` - Landing page for deployment

## Development
- Frontend dev: `npm run dev:h5`
- Backend dev: `cd backend && npm run dev`
- Both run on: localhost:5173 (frontend) and localhost:3000 (backend)

## Deployment
- Website: Netlify (website/ folder)
- Backend: Railway (recommended)
- Frontend App: Vercel (recommended)

